      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GINNY'S RUN (4) missed the hat-trick last start when second and beaten 1.75 lengths (43.67) last time at this track. Solid record at the distance winning five races. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Expected to feature in the finish again. CANYA VIVI (8) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fourth (35.20) in a Other at this track. Good beginner but will need a little luck early crossing from an outside draw. Has ability and is one of the better chances. WILMA'S OUR GIRL (1) overcame a check to finish in the minors of a Grade 6/MDN last time (35.21) at this track over 595m. Has the ability and can measure up. CORRYONG (2) placed last time and cannot be ignored.",
